arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_KILLBIG, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_attach")
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(SWITCH_BRAZIER, true)
	Hydra.SetGameVariableFlag("QST_Frac_Brazier_Lit_DuringVGN")
end

arCallbackSets.szOnSetCompleteScript:
Hydra.Wait(1) --Give a quick breath at the end of a wave
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_KILLBIG, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_attach")
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE2_N)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE2_NW)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE2_NE)

Hydra.Wait(1) --Give a quick breath at the end of a wave
Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_KILLBIG, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_attach")
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE3_N)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE3_NW)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE3_NE)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE3_SW)
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(SPAWNER_WAVE3_SE)

arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_KILLBIG, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_attach")
	--Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(MARKER_FIRE, FireFX)
	Hydra.ActorFlagDynamicPrefabGroupForDespawn(idSelf)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idActorKilled, 4)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idActorKilled, 1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorKilled, MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_ATTRACTOR, false, "Default", "HP_HEAD")
	Hydra.Wait(1.0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(MARKER_FIRE, EFFECT_GROUP_KILLSMALL, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_attach")
end
